      "caption": "mwb26 Mayo p. 12-13",
      "content": "<header>\r\n<h1 class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-color--textSubdued\" id=\"p1\" data-pid=\"1\"><span id=\"page12\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"12\" data-before-text=\"12\"></span>HUNYO 15-21</h1>\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-margin-top--2 du-margin-top-desktopOnly--4\" id=\"p2\" data-pid=\"2\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>JEREMIAS 7-8</strong></a></h2>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"bodyTxt\">\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p3\" data-pid=\"3\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/0/0\"><strong>Awit 152</strong></a> <strong>ug Pag-ampo | Introduksiyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(1 min.)</span></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt7\" class=\"du-fontSize--basePlus2 dc-icon--gem dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--teal-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p4\" data-pid=\"4\"><strong>BAHANDI GIKAN SA PULONG SA DIYOS</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt9\" class=\"dc-bleedToArticleEdge dc-paddingToContentEdge du-bgColor--bgSecondary du-margin-top--8 du-padding-top--8 du-padding-bottom--1\">\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p5\" data-pid=\"5\"><strong>1. Gipasipalahan Nila ang Templo ni Jehova</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt11\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt12\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p6\" data-pid=\"6\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p id=\"p7\" data-pid=\"7\">Nagtuo ang daghang taga-Juda nga ang templo makapanalipod nila bisag daotan silag binuhatan (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 7:4,</a><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 8-10</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/1/0\"><em>jr</em> 21 ¶12</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p8\" data-pid=\"8\">Ang ilang binuhatan nagpasipala sa ngalan ni Jehova (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 7:11</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/2/0\"><em>it</em> “Jehova” ¶78</a>)</p>\r\n<p id=\"p9\" data-pid=\"9\">Gigamit ni Jehova ingong pananglitan ang Shilo aron ipakita kon unsay mahitabo sa templo (<a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 7:12-14</a>; <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/3/0\"><em>it</em> “Shilo” Num. 2 ¶4</a>)</p>\r\n<hr class=\"du-width--oneSixth du-borderWidth--1 du-borderColor--borderDefault\"/>\r\n<p id=\"p10\" data-pid=\"10\"><span class=\"du-color--teal-700\"><strong>PANGUTAN-A ANG KAUGALINGON,</strong></span> ‘Ang ako bang binuhatan nagpasidungog kang Jehova sa tanang panahon?’</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f1\" class=\"south_center\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/220\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/219\" alt=\"Collage: 1. Gisinggitan sa usa ka brader ang iyang katrabaho. 2. Buotang gitimbaya sa mao ra gihapon nga brader ang laing brader diha sa Kingdom Hall.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" class=\"south_center\" />\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p11\" data-pid=\"11\"><strong>2. Espirituwal nga mga Bahandi</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt15\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt16\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p12\" data-pid=\"12\">(10 min.)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul class=\"du-listStyleType--none du-padding-inlineStart--0\"><li><p id=\"p13\" data-pid=\"13\"><a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/4/0\" data-bid=\"5-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 8:22</a>—Niini nga teksto, unsay gipasabot sa ‘walay balsamo sa Gilead’? (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/4/0\"><em>jr</em> 135 ¶14</a>)</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p14\" data-pid=\"14\">\r\n<label for=\"tt21\" id=\"tt19\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt21\" name=\"textarea-1\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p15\" data-pid=\"15\">Unsang espirituwal nga mga bahandi ang imong nakat-onan sa pagbasa sa Bibliya niining semanaha?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p16\" data-pid=\"16\">\r\n<label for=\"tt26\" id=\"tt24\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt26\" name=\"textarea-2\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--teal-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p17\" data-pid=\"17\"><strong>3. Pagbasa sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt29\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p18\" data-pid=\"18\">(4 min.) <a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/5/0\" data-bid=\"6-1\" class=\"b\">Jer 8:4-13</a> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/5/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 2</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt30\" class=\"dc-icon--wheat dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--gold-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p19\" data-pid=\"19\"><strong>MAGMAEPEKTIBO SA MINISTERYO</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p20\" data-pid=\"20\"><strong>4. Dihang Magsugod ug Panag-estorya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt33\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p21\" data-pid=\"21\">(3 min.) IMPORMAL NGA PAGSANGYAW. (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/6/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 5 punto 5</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p22\" data-pid=\"22\"><strong>5. Dihang Makig-estorya Pag-usab</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt35\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p23\" data-pid=\"23\">(4 min.) PAGPAMALAYBALAY. Paghisgot ug kamatuoran gikan sa <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/7/0\">apendise A</a> sa brosyur nga <em>Higugmaa ang mga Tawo.</em> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/8/0\"><em>lmd</em> leksiyon 9 punto 3</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--gold-700 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p24\" data-pid=\"24\"><strong>6. Dihang Maghimog Tinun-an</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt37\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p25\" data-pid=\"25\">(5 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/9/0\"><em>lff</em> leksiyon 19 punto 6</a> (<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/10/0\"><em>th</em> tun-anan 19</a>)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt38\" class=\"dc-icon--sheep dc-icon-layout--top dc-icon-bgColor--red-600 dc-icon-color--white dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8 dc-icon-padding--5 dc-icon-size--baseMinus1 du-fontSize--basePlus2 du-borderStyle-bottom--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--1 du-margin-top--12 du-margin-bottom--2 du-padding-bottom--2\">\r\n<h2 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-vertical--0\" id=\"p26\" data-pid=\"26\"><span id=\"page13\" class=\"pageNum\" aria-hidden=\"true\" data-no=\"13\" data-before-text=\"13\"></span><strong>KRISTOHANONG PAGKINABUHI</strong></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-horizontal--8 du-fontSize--base\" id=\"p27\" data-pid=\"27\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/11/0\"><strong>Awit 91</strong></a></h3>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p28\" data-pid=\"28\"><strong>7. Kon Unsaon Pagpakita nga Gipabilhan Nato ang Atong mga Kingdom Hall</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt43\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p29\" data-pid=\"29\">(5 min.) Pakighisgot.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"f2\" class=\"north_center\">\r\n<figure>\r\n<img src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/222\" data-img-small-src=\"/wol/mp/r101/lp-cv/mwb26/2026/221\" alt=\"Esena gikan sa video nga “Mahimong Higala ni Jehova​—⁠Mahala ang Balay ni Jehova.” Gitrapohan ni Caleb ang usa ka lingkoranan sa Kingdom Hall.\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" class=\"north_center\" />\r\n</figure>\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"tt44\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<p id=\"p30\" data-pid=\"30\"><a href=\"https://www.jw.org/finder?wtlocale=CV&amp;lank=pub-pk_31_VIDEO\" data-video=\"webpubvid://?pub=pk&amp;track=31&amp;langwritten=CV\"><strong>I-play ang VIDEO</strong></a> <strong>nga <em>Mahimong Higala ni Jehova—Mahala ang Balay ni Jehova.</em></strong> Dayon pangutan-a ang mamiminaw:</p>\r\n<ul><li><p id=\"p31\" data-pid=\"31\">  Unsaon nato pag-atiman ang Kingdom Hall, ug nganong kanay atong himoon?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p32\" data-pid=\"32\">\r\n<label for=\"tt50\" id=\"tt48\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt50\" name=\"textarea-3\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p id=\"p33\" data-pid=\"33\"><span class=\"du-color--maroon-600\"><strong>Basaha ang</strong></span> <a href=\"/wol/bc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/6/0\" data-bid=\"7-1\" class=\"b\"><strong>1 Timoteo 2:9, 10</strong></a><strong>.</strong> Dayon pangutan-a ang mamiminaw:</p>\r\n<ul><li><p id=\"p34\" data-pid=\"34\">  Unsa pay laing paagi nga atong mapakita nga gitahod nato si Jehova dihang motambong ta sa tigom?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p35\" data-pid=\"35\">\r\n<label for=\"tt57\" id=\"tt55\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt57\" name=\"textarea-4\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p36\" data-pid=\"36\"><strong>8. Kon Giunsa Paggamit ang Inyong Donasyon—Pagmentinar sa Atong mga Kingdom Hall</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt60\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6\">\r\n<div id=\"tt61\" class=\"du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p37\" data-pid=\"37\">(10 min.) Pakighisgot base sa artikulo. Hisgoti ang mga galastohan sa pagmentinar sa inyong Kingdom Hall.—<a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/12/0\"><em>hdu</em> artikulo 30</a>.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<ul><li><p id=\"p38\" data-pid=\"38\">  Unsa nga mga galastohan ang kinahanglang himoon aron magpabiling maayo ang kondisyon sa mga Kingdom Hall, ug nganong importante ni nga buluhaton?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p39\" data-pid=\"39\">\r\n<label for=\"tt66\" id=\"tt64\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt66\" name=\"textarea-5\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p40\" data-pid=\"40\">  Unsay imong naapresyar sa pagkaorganisado sa dagkong mga proyekto sa pagmentinar ug sa pondo nga gigamit para ani?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p41\" data-pid=\"41\">\r\n<label for=\"tt71\" id=\"tt69\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt71\" name=\"textarea-6\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"du-margin-top--8\"><p id=\"p42\" data-pid=\"42\">  Unsay imong ikatabang?</p>\r\n<div class=\"gen-field\" id=\"p43\" data-pid=\"43\">\r\n<label for=\"tt76\" id=\"tt74\" class=\"dc-screenReaderText\">Imong tubag</label>\r\n<textarea id=\"tt76\" name=\"textarea-7\"></textarea>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<hr class=\"du-width--oneSixth du-borderWidth--1 du-borderColor--borderDefault du-margin-top--12\"/>\r\n<div id=\"tt78\">\r\n<p id=\"p44\" data-pid=\"44\">Para sa dugang impormasyon kon sa unsang paagi ka makaamot, i-click ang “<a href=\"https://donate.jw.org/\">Donations</a>” nga icon sa ubos sa home page sa <em>JW Library</em><sup>®</sup> nga app o sa jw.org.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-color--maroon-600 du-margin-top--8 du-margin-bottom--0\" id=\"p45\" data-pid=\"45\"><strong>9. Pagtuon sa Kongregasyon sa Bibliya</strong></h3>\r\n<div id=\"tt80\" class=\"du-margin-inlineStart--5 du-margin-inlineStart-desktopOnly--6 du-color--textSubdued du-margin-top--1 du-margin-children-vertical--0\">\r\n<p id=\"p46\" data-pid=\"46\">(30 min.) <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/13/0\"><em>lfb</em> intro sa seksiyon 14</a> ug <a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/14/0\">leksiyon 94-95</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3 class=\"du-fontSize--base du-borderStyle-top--solid du-borderColor--borderDefault du-borderWidth--2 du-margin-top--12 du-padding-top--4 du-padding-top-desktopOnly--5\" id=\"p47\" data-pid=\"47\"><strong>Konklusyon</strong> <span class=\"du-fontWeight--normal\">(3 min.)</span> <strong>|</strong> <span class=\"dc-icon--music dc-icon-size--basePlus1 dc-icon-margin-inlineStart--2 dc-icon-margin-inlineEnd--8\"><a href=\"/wol/pc/r101/lp-cv/202026167/15/0\"><strong>Awit 71</strong></a></span> <strong>ug Pag-ampo</strong></h3>\r\n</div>\r\n",
